    <item>
      <title>中国誓言回应加拿大因涉嫌侵犯人权而实施的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-vows-response-to-canada-sanctions-for-alleged-rights-abuse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国谴责加拿大因涉嫌侵犯人权而对八名中国官员实施制裁，这导致本已紧张的双边关系出现新的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-vows-response-to-canada-sanctions-for-alleged-rights-abuse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将对威胁限制香港的美国官员实施签证限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-to-restrict-visas-to-us-officials-for-threatening-hk-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，将对涉嫌干预香港事务的一些美国官员实施签证限制，这一针锋相对的举措凸显了唐纳德·特朗普上任前亚洲金融中心的地缘政治紧张局势加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-to-restrict-visas-to-us-officials-for-threatening-hk-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿萨德倒台震动伊朗日益脆弱的领导层</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/is-iran-next-fall-of-assad-jolts-a-vulnerable-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普准备重返白宫，伊朗伊斯兰共和国的“抵抗轴心”被打破，政权陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/is-iran-next-fall-of-assad-jolts-a-vulnerable-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行认为缅甸内战持续加剧，经济萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/world-bank-sees-myanmar-economy-shrinking-as-civil-war-rages-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行预计，缅甸经济将在本财年萎缩，因为通货膨胀率上升、货币贬值以及电力和劳动力短缺进一步给这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/world-bank-sees-myanmar-economy-shrinking-as-civil-war-rages-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>令人震惊的 CEO 谋杀案的逮捕仍留下关键问题悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/arrest-in-shock-ceo-murder-still-leaves-key-questions-unanswered</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，路易吉·曼吉奥内 (Luigi Mangione) 因枪杀联合健康集团高管布莱恩·汤普森 (Brian Thompson) 而被捕，但这未能填补这起震惊美国的凶杀案的一些关键细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/arrest-in-shock-ceo-murder-still-leaves-key-questions-unanswered</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:25:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾表示将继续进行调查，因为杜特尔特跳过了质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-says-probe-to-go-ahead-as-duterte-skips-questioning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特周三第二次未出面接受问询，她曾威胁称，如果她被杀，总统费迪南德·马科斯小将被暗杀。菲律宾国家调查局将继续调查这一事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-says-probe-to-go-ahead-as-duterte-skips-questioning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚政权垮台后俄罗斯非洲战略面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/syria-russia-s-africa-strategy-hanging-by-a-thread-after-regime-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚巴沙尔·阿萨德政权的迅速垮台对俄罗斯在叙利亚的一个重要空军基地构成威胁，莫斯科一直依赖该基地向整个非洲施加影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/syria-russia-s-africa-strategy-hanging-by-a-thread-after-regime-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着调查的深入，韩国的尹永哲寻求继续战斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着韩国总统尹锡烈戒严宣言的调查不断深入，且另一起弹劾案即将出现，他似乎准备继续战斗，而不是提前下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将阻止新日铁交易，美国钢铁价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-set-to-finally-kill-nippon-steel-s-proposed-takeover-of-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，一旦本月晚些时候交易被交回给拜登，拜登总统计划以国家安全为由正式阻止美国钢铁公司以 141 亿美元的价格出售给新日本制铁公司的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-set-to-finally-kill-nippon-steel-s-proposed-takeover-of-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
